## Docker Compose Stack

All services run via Docker Compose at `/home/ibbot/ib_bot`.
Production uses two compose files: `docker-compose.yml` + `docker-compose.prod.yml`.

| Service | Container | Internal Port |
|---------|-----------|---------------|
| PostgreSQL 16 | ib_bot-db-1 | 5432 |
| Redis 7 | ib_bot-redis-1 | 6379 |
| FastAPI API | ib_bot-api-1 | 8000 |
| Celery Worker | ib_bot-worker-1 | -- |
| Celery Beat | ib_bot-beat-1 | -- |
| Next.js Frontend | ib_bot-web-1 | 3000 |
| nginx | ib_bot-nginx-1 | 80, 443 |

